Fix: manager: file descriptor leakage

commit.message:
Fix: manager: file descriptor leakage

Manager leaks pipes used for waking up from poll() when SIGCHLD is
received.

This mechanism is removed since it is unnecessary. When a child process
ends, its stdin/stdout/stderr will be closed, waking the parent up from
poll().

Fix #17.
